My upcoming travel will be to Magdeburg and Berlin. I am planning to start my vacation next Monday. First I will be going to Magdeburg to meet my friends. Later I will be visiting Berlin and Potsdam along with my friends. I plan to stay a week and enjoy the vibes of Berlin.

After my completion of project I am planning to go to the Netherlands for vacation. I look forward to enjoy the food and nightlife of Amsterdam. I am very eager to learn the many ways how Dutch have mastered the wind energy. I would also love to explore Rotterdam if time permits.
